|-------|----------|-------------|
| **V2 — Assistant** | Month 2 | Agents can execute with merchant approval. "Apply all" button. Undo/rollback. |
| **V3 — Autopilot** | Month 4 | Per-agent autonomy settings. Agents act overnight, report in morning. Trust scores. |
