## Common Issues & Fixes

| Issue | Cause | Fix |
|-------|-------|-----|
| Agent not discovered | Registry not updated | Dev commits agent, Lead adds to registry |
| Findings not saving | Executor not called | Verify route action calls agentExecutor.execute() |
