```

### 4.3 Status Badges

```jsx
const statusTones = {
  "Pending": "info",
  "In Progress": "warning",
  "Approved": "success",
  "Dismissed": "subdued",
  "Failed": "critical",
};

<s-badge tone={statusTones[status]}>
  {status}
</s-badge>
```

